-- > INGEN INTERNAL CASE FILE #00211-1976 [WONAMBI NARACOORTENSIS] CODENAME: RIVERSLEIGH >932
Wonambi was a genus of non-venomous, constrictor snakes, and seems to have been an ambush predator that killed its prey by constriction. The head of the animal was small, restricting the size of its prey.
